eft" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&#x0003c;0.001</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><strong>4. Playgrounds perceived as very clean or clean</strong></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Primary</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">72.2% (366/507)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">61.6% (415/674)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><strong>&#x0003c;0.001</strong></td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Secondary</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">56.5% (444/786)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">53.5% (386/721)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.25</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><strong>5. Classrooms perceived as very clean or clean</strong></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Primary</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">73.6% (374/508)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">68.5% (462/674)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.058</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Secondary</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">51.3% (404/787)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">52.5% (380/724)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.65</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1"><strong>6. Toilets perceived as very clean or clean</strong></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td><td rowspan="1" colspan="1"></td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Primary</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">34.7% (176/507)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">38.5% (259/673)</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">0.18</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Secondary</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan=